@startuml seq-19-admin-user-create
title POST /admin/users — create user (admin)

actor "Administrator" as A <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/admin" as API <<service>>
participant "authenticateToken +\nrequireRole(ADMIN)" as MW <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

B -> API: POST /admin/users\n{ email, password, name, role, departmentId, … }

API -> MW: authorize
API -> API: Zod createUserBody;\nvalidate EMPLOYEE needs badge
API -> DB: findUnique email — conflict?
API -> DB: department + role lookups
alt Validation / conflict
  API --> B: 400 / 409
else OK
  API -> API: hashPassword
  API -> DB: $transaction:\n user.create\n userDepartmentAccess.create\n(MANAGER→MANAGER level else MEMBER)
  alt Prisma P2002 unique
    API --> B: 409 badge/email
  else Success
    API --> B: 201 { user }
  end
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/admin.ts** (~569+).
end note

@enduml
